quran[10{c,v,t}:
20,126,khuda farmaiye ga ke aisa hi ( chahiye tha ) tairay paas meri ayatain ayen to tunay un ko bhala diya. isi terhan aaj hum tujh ko bhala den ge
20,127,aur jo shakhs hadd se nikal jaye aur apne perwar-digaar ki aayton par imaan nah laaye hum is ko aisa hi badla dete hain. aur akhirat ka azaab bohat sakht aur bohat der rehne wala hai
20,128,kiya yeh baat un logon ke liye mojab hadaayat nah hui ke hum un se pehlay bohat se logon ko halaak kar chukay hain jin ke rehne ke maqamat mein yeh chaltay phirtay hain. aqal walon ke liye is mein ( bohat si ) nishanain hain
20,129,aur agar aik baat tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se pehlay sadir aur ( jzaye aamaal ke liye ) aik meyaad muqarrar nah hochuki hoti to ( nuzool ) azaab lazim hojata
20,130,pas jo kuch yeh bakwaas karte hain is par sabr karo. aur Sooraj ke niklny se pehlay aur is ke ghuroob honay se pehlay apne perwar-digaar ki tasbeeh tahmeed kiya karo. aur raat ki saa-at ( awaleen ) mein bhi is ki tasbeehkiya karo aur din ki atraaf ( yani dopehar ke qareeb Zahar ke waqt bhi ) taakay tum khush hojao
20,131,aur kayi terhan ke logon ko jo hum ne duniya ki zindagi mein Araish ki cheezon se behra mandkiya hai taakay un ki azmaish karen un par nigah nah karna. aur tumhari perwar-digaar ki ( ataa farmai hui ) rozi bohat behtar aur baqi rehne wali hai
20,132,aur apne ghar walon ko namaz ka hukum karo aur is par qaim raho. hum tum se rozi ke khawastgah nahi. balkay tumhe hum rozi dete hain aur ( naik ) injaam ( ahal ) taqwa ka hai
20,133,aur kehte hain ke yeh ( paighambar ) apne perwar-digaar ki taraf se hamaray paas koi nishani kyun nahi laatay.kiya un ke paas pehli kitabon ki nishani nahi aayi ?
20,134,aur agar hum un ko paighambar ( ke bhejnay ) se peshtar kisi azaab se halaak kardete to woh kehte ke ae hamaray perwar-digaar to ne hamari taraf koi paighambar kyun nah bheja ke hum zaleel aur ruswa honay se pehlay tairay kalaam (o ahkaam ) ki pairwi karte
20,135,keh do ke sab ( nataij aamaal ) ke munhtazir hain so tum bhi munhtazir raho. anqareeb tum ko maloom hojaye ga ke ( deen ke ) seedhay raste par chalne walay kon hain aur ( jannat ki taraf ) raah panay walay kon hain ( hum ya tum )
